<title>ḥytẖmạ ạ̉kwn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥytẖmạ ạ̉kwn lst ạ̉bgẖy ly swạk
 dạỷmaⁿạ fy rfqty tqwdny ydạk
 ạ̉nt ḥṣny wrjạỷy ạ̹n ḍllt ywmaⁿạ
 mbtgẖạy ṭwl ʿmry msẖthạy dwmaⁿạ
 ạlqrạr- (yswʿ yswʿ .. yswʿ yswʿ)2
 2- sạ̉frḥ bḥbk fhw ly ạlḍmạn
 mn ydry by gẖyrk yạ mạlk ạlkyạn
 yṭyb ly ạ̉n ạ̉drk kyf tʿwd tḥyyny
 fḥynmạ ạljw ygẖym ḥḍnk yḍmny</lyrics>
</song>